3.text: Sathish : Madhavan, have you got a pet dog? Madhavan : No, we haven't. We haven't got any place to keep dogs. Sathish : Haven't you got a garden? Madhavan : We have a garden but it's too small to keep a dog. Sathish : Do you have any other pets at home? Madhavan : No. I don't have any at home but I love watching birds.
